<view class="page">
  <view class="hero">
    <view class="badge">🛒 InfiniSynapse</view>
    <view class="title">省钱比价助手</view>
    <view class="subtitle">让 AI 帮你跨平台比价、读差评、算券后到手价，少花冤枉钱。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="feature">
      <view class="feature-item">
        <text class="feature-emoji">💰</text>
        <text>券后到手价，满减运费一起算</text>
      </view>
      <view class="feature-item">
        <text class="feature-emoji">🔀</text>
        <text>京东、淘宝、天猫同款比价</text>
      </view>
      <view class="feature-item">
        <text class="feature-emoji">🛡️</text>
        <text>差评追评先看，避坑不踩雷</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card login-card">
    <view wx:if="{{step === 'login'}}">
      <view class="step-title">第 1 步 · 登录账号</view>
      <view class="muted">使用微信快速登录，并关联你的 InfiniSynapse 账号。</view>
      <button class="btn btn-dark login-btn" loading="{{logging}}" bindtap="doWxLogin">
        微信一键登录
      </button>
    </view>

    <view wx:if="{{step === 'phone'}}">
      <view class="step-title">第 2 步 · 授权手机号</view>
      <view class="muted">通过手机号关联你在 InfiniSynapse 的账号。我们只用于账号匹配。</view>
      <button
        class="btn btn-primary login-btn"
        open-type="getPhoneNumber"
        loading="{{binding}}"
        bindgetphonenumber="onGetPhone"
      >
        授权手机号并继续
      </button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="footer muted">
    AI 购物实际在 PC 端 Chrome 中执行，登录后会引导你完成。
  </view>
</view>
